Storyboarding Andvanced v01


How to use:


With this workflow, you can turn your scribbles and storyboard panels into final images in any style!


I have tested this workflow mainly with the wildcard XL model, but any other model will work as well. Just remember to adjust the sampler settings to the respective model. Also don't forget to adjust the controlnet model if you want to use an SD15 model, for example.


You can find the model here: Wildcard Turbo XL.


If you're having problems:


Don't expect it to work every time the first time. Be precise in your prompts and try out different seeds in the kSampler.


Post Screenshots of your error messages and workflow in the #need-help channel in our Community Discord. You will be automatically invited when you join my Patreon.


Feel free to share your creations in our community Discord #show-your-work.

You can use an image as a style reference here. Deactivate the group if you don't need it and prompt for your style in the master prompts.


All ipAdapters in this workflow are optional! Deacticvate them if you don't need them.

For SDXL models use: mistoLine_rank256.safetensors

Place here: \ComfyUI_windows_portable\ComfyUI\models\controlnet\sdxl

For SD15 you can try out Canny, Scribble and lineArt. You can find the models in the ComfyUI Model Manager.

If you're using upscale models like 4x-ClearReality you can bring down the overall upscaling of the image down with the "upscale image by" node. In my case I wanted to upscale 2x so I used 0.50 there.


Use Denoise between 0.15 and 0.5.

Here you can change the characters emotion. Deactivate if you don't need it! Make sure to match the settings to your model. This is adjusted for the Wildcard model.


Use Denoise between 0.15 and 0.5. A higher denoise value changes the emotion more strongly.
I deactivated all optional nodes! Select them and use CNTR+B to activate.
